[
  {
    "start": 0.16,
    "end": 5.92,
    "text": "",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1.92,
    "end": 10.4,
    "text": "Welcome to English Daily Channel.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 5.92,
    "end": 15.92,
    "text": " Tom, you look worried. What happened?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 10.4,
    "end": 19.279,
    "text": " Ashley, I have a problem. A big problem.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 15.92,
    "end": 21.279,
    "text": " Okay, tell me what is it?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 19.279,
    "end": 24.16,
    "text": " I went outside",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 21.279,
    "end": 28.56,
    "text": "and I forgot my key.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 24.16,
    "end": 33.52,
    "text": " You forgot your key? Oh, no. Yes, I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 28.56,
    "end": 37.12,
    "text": "closed the door. Now the key is inside.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 33.52,
    "end": 40.719,
    "text": " Oh, you locked yourself out.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 37.12,
    "end": 42.32,
    "text": " Yes, I locked myself out. And it gets",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 40.719,
    "end": 45.52,
    "text": "worse.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 42.32,
    "end": 49.12,
    "text": " Worse? What do you mean?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 45.52,
    "end": 52.48,
    "text": " My phone is also inside.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 49.12,
    "end": 56.96,
    "text": " No key and no phone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 52.48,
    "end": 59.039,
    "text": " Exactly. I can't open the door. I can't",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 56.96,
    "end": 61.359,
    "text": "call anyone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 59.039,
    "end": 65.519,
    "text": " What about your roommate?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 61.359,
    "end": 70.4,
    "text": " He will come back tonight. Very late.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 65.519,
    "end": 73.84,
    "text": " So, you can't go in until tonight.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 70.4,
    "end": 78.08,
    "text": " Yes. What should I do?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 73.84,
    "end": 80.0,
    "text": " Well, you have one free day now.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 78.08,
    "end": 85.36,
    "text": " Free day?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 80.0,
    "end": 90.24,
    "text": "I feel nervous. No phone, no key.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 85.36,
    "end": 93.119,
    "text": "Don't worry. Maybe this is a good thing.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 90.24,
    "end": 97.2,
    "text": " A good thing? Really?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 93.119,
    "end": 98.88,
    "text": " Yes. You can try one day without a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 97.2,
    "end": 102.64,
    "text": "phone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 98.88,
    "end": 104.079,
    "text": " One day without a phone. That sounds",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 102.64,
    "end": 108.72,
    "text": "scary.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 104.079,
    "end": 110.399,
    "text": " It can be fun. We can go out. We can see",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 108.72,
    "end": 114.799,
    "text": "things.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 110.399,
    "end": 118.159,
    "text": " Go out. Where can we go?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 114.799,
    "end": 120.479,
    "text": "Let's start with the library.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 118.159,
    "end": 124.079,
    "text": " The library.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 120.479,
    "end": 126.479,
    "text": "Okay. But how can we go?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 124.079,
    "end": 130.479,
    "text": " We can take the bus.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 126.479,
    "end": 132.0,
    "text": " The bus? But I need Uber. I need my",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 130.479,
    "end": 136.959,
    "text": "phone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 132.0,
    "end": 141.92,
    "text": " Not today. Today we use the bus.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 136.959,
    "end": 145.04,
    "text": " Okay, let's try. No phone, no key, just",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 141.92,
    "end": 149.44,
    "text": "the bus. Here",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 145.04,
    "end": 151.12,
    "text": "we are. This is the bus stop for the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 149.44,
    "end": 154.319,
    "text": "library.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 151.12,
    "end": 158.8,
    "text": " The bus stop for the library.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 154.319,
    "end": 161.68,
    "text": " Yes, we wait here for the bus.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 158.8,
    "end": 166.16,
    "text": " Okay, we wait here.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 161.68,
    "end": 169.28,
    "text": " Look, the bus is coming now.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 166.16,
    "end": 174.08,
    "text": " Good. I was getting nervous.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 169.28,
    "end": 176.4,
    "text": " Why nervous? Because without my phone, I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 174.08,
    "end": 180.959,
    "text": "don't know the time.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 176.4,
    "end": 184.8,
    "text": " Yes, no phone means no clock.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 180.959,
    "end": 186.319,
    "text": " Right. I usually check the bus time on",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 184.8,
    "end": 189.92,
    "text": "my phone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 186.319,
    "end": 191.599,
    "text": " Today you learn another way.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 189.92,
    "end": 196.879,
    "text": " Another way.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 191.599,
    "end": 200.48,
    "text": " Yes. Just look at the bus stop sign.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 196.879,
    "end": 201.76,
    "text": " Look at the bus stop sign.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 200.48,
    "end": 205.68,
    "text": "Okay,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 201.76,
    "end": 208.72,
    "text": " now let's get on the bus.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 205.68,
    "end": 212.08,
    "text": " All right, let's get on.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 208.72,
    "end": 213.519,
    "text": " Say, \"One ticket to the library,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 212.08,
    "end": 217.12,
    "text": "please.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 213.519,
    "end": 220.959,
    "text": " One ticket to the library, please.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 217.12,
    "end": 225.44,
    "text": " Perfect. Now, take the ticket.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 220.959,
    "end": 231.92,
    "text": " Got it. One ticket to the library.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 225.44,
    "end": 234.319,
    "text": " Good. Now, where should we sit? Hm. Here",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 231.92,
    "end": 237.04,
    "text": "or near the window?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 234.319,
    "end": 240.72,
    "text": " I like the window seat.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 237.04,
    "end": 243.92,
    "text": " Okay, let's sit near the window.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 240.72,
    "end": 245.76,
    "text": " Great. Sit down.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 243.92,
    "end": 249.519,
    "text": " All right.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 245.76,
    "end": 252.0,
    "text": "Wow. It feels strange.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 249.519,
    "end": 256.56,
    "text": " Strange? Why?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 252.0,
    "end": 258.4,
    "text": " Because everyone is on the phone, but I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 256.56,
    "end": 259.44,
    "text": "have no phone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 258.4,
    "end": 263.68,
    "text": " Yes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 259.44,
    "end": 266.8,
    "text": "Many people just look at their phones.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 263.68,
    "end": 268.16,
    "text": " I feel a little nervous. What should I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 266.8,
    "end": 270.08,
    "text": "do?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 268.16,
    "end": 271.52,
    "text": " Look outside.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 270.08,
    "end": 276.8,
    "text": " Look outside.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 271.52,
    "end": 280.8,
    "text": " Yes. Look at the trees, the buildings.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 276.8,
    "end": 284.24,
    "text": " Okay. Oh, nice view.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 280.8,
    "end": 288.479,
    "text": " Better than a small screen, right?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 284.24,
    "end": 293.44,
    "text": " Yes. Better than a small screen. See,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 288.479,
    "end": 297.12,
    "text": "without a phone, you can see the world.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 293.44,
    "end": 302.32,
    "text": " See the world? I like that.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 297.12,
    "end": 306.639,
    "text": " And you can also talk to me.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 302.32,
    "end": 310.72,
    "text": " Yes. Talk to you, not the phone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 306.639,
    "end": 311.919,
    "text": " Remember, we get off at the library",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 310.72,
    "end": 315.84,
    "text": "stop.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 311.919,
    "end": 318.4,
    "text": " We get off at the library stop, right?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 315.84,
    "end": 321.84,
    "text": " Yes. That's right.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 318.4,
    "end": 323.28,
    "text": " Okay. The library stop. Don't let me",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 321.84,
    "end": 326.8,
    "text": "miss it.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 323.28,
    "end": 332.0,
    "text": " Don't worry. I will tell you.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 326.8,
    "end": 334.24,
    "text": " Good. Without my phone, I feel lost, but",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 332.0,
    "end": 338.16,
    "text": "also free.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 334.24,
    "end": 342.639,
    "text": " Lost and free. That's interesting.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 338.16,
    "end": 346.8,
    "text": " Yes. It's new for me, but maybe it's",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 342.639,
    "end": 350.72,
    "text": "good. You're learning something today.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 346.8,
    "end": 353.28,
    "text": " Yes. One day without a phone, it's not",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 350.72,
    "end": 357.52,
    "text": "so bad.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 353.28,
    "end": 362.24,
    "text": " Here we are. This is the library.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 357.52,
    "end": 366.96,
    "text": " Wow, it's big and very quiet.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 362.24,
    "end": 368.319,
    "text": " Yes, it's a quiet place for reading and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 366.96,
    "end": 371.68,
    "text": "studying.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 368.319,
    "end": 373.199,
    "text": " Reading and studying.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 371.68,
    "end": 378.16,
    "text": "No noise,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 373.199,
    "end": 379.919,
    "text": " right? No noise. People come here to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 378.16,
    "end": 383.759,
    "text": "focus.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 379.919,
    "end": 385.28,
    "text": " Focus. You mean to pay attention.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 383.759,
    "end": 389.039,
    "text": " Exactly.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 385.28,
    "end": 392.96,
    "text": "To pay attention and learn.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 389.039,
    "end": 396.4,
    "text": " Okay. I will try to focus too.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 392.96,
    "end": 400.319,
    "text": " Good. Let's go inside.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 396.4,
    "end": 404.8,
    "text": " All right. Inside the library.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 400.319,
    "end": 408.639,
    "text": "Look, so many books on the shelves.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 404.8,
    "end": 409.6,
    "text": " Yes, so many. I don't know where to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 408.639,
    "end": 413.52,
    "text": "start.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 409.6,
    "end": 416.56,
    "text": " Let's find something about cooking.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 413.52,
    "end": 421.28,
    "text": " Cooking in the library?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 416.56,
    "end": 422.8,
    "text": " Yes, there are books for everything.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 421.28,
    "end": 427.68,
    "text": " Everything?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 422.8,
    "end": 430.639,
    "text": "You mean also cooking? Yes. Cooking,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 427.68,
    "end": 432.4,
    "text": "travel, history,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 430.639,
    "end": 437.599,
    "text": "everything.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 432.4,
    "end": 441.84,
    "text": " Wow. Not only novels. That's new for me.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 437.599,
    "end": 445.919,
    "text": " Here, let me take one book down.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 441.84,
    "end": 449.039,
    "text": " Okay. One book about cooking.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 445.919,
    "end": 453.36,
    "text": " Let's sit here by the window.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 449.039,
    "end": 457.44,
    "text": " Nice table. The sunlight is warm.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 453.36,
    "end": 461.84,
    "text": "Yes. It feels comfortable.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 457.44,
    "end": 466.24,
    "text": " Comfortable? You mean good and easy?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 461.84,
    "end": 468.96,
    "text": " Exactly. Good and easy.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 466.24,
    "end": 470.24,
    "text": " All right. I like this comfortable",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 468.96,
    "end": 474.639,
    "text": "place.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 470.24,
    "end": 476.4,
    "text": " Now, look at this page. It explains a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 474.639,
    "end": 477.919,
    "text": "recipe.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 476.4,
    "end": 480.72,
    "text": " Recipe.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 477.919,
    "end": 485.36,
    "text": "That's a plan for food, right?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 480.72,
    "end": 490.319,
    "text": " Yes. A plan for food. A recipe.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 485.36,
    "end": 495.12,
    "text": " Okay, I want to read the recipe slowly.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 490.319,
    "end": 496.8,
    "text": "Ashley, this is nice. I can read without",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 495.12,
    "end": 502.24,
    "text": "my phone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 496.8,
    "end": 504.639,
    "text": " See, books can give full information.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 502.24,
    "end": 507.12,
    "text": " Full information,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 504.639,
    "end": 513.839,
    "text": "not just small pieces,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 507.12,
    "end": 516.479,
    "text": " right? Not small pieces. full and clear.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 513.839,
    "end": 518.159,
    "text": " I feel calm.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 516.479,
    "end": 523.519,
    "text": "Very calm.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 518.159,
    "end": 529.44,
    "text": " Yes, the library makes you calm.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 523.519,
    "end": 532.64,
    "text": " Now I enjoy reading. I really enjoy it.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 529.44,
    "end": 534.399,
    "text": " That's great, Tom. You see the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 532.64,
    "end": 540.399,
    "text": "difference now?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 534.399,
    "end": 542.24,
    "text": " Yes, I see it. No phone, just books.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 540.399,
    "end": 546.56,
    "text": "Exactly.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 542.24,
    "end": 551.6,
    "text": "No phone, just books.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 546.56,
    "end": 553.2,
    "text": "We read a lot, Tom. Do your eyes feel",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 551.6,
    "end": 556.959,
    "text": "tired?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 553.2,
    "end": 561.04,
    "text": " Yes, a little tired.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 556.959,
    "end": 566.16,
    "text": " Then let's rest our eyes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 561.04,
    "end": 567.68,
    "text": " Rest our eyes? You mean stop reading?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 566.16,
    "end": 570.88,
    "text": " Exactly.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 567.68,
    "end": 572.64,
    "text": "Let's go outside.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 570.88,
    "end": 573.839,
    "text": " Outside",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 572.64,
    "end": 579.04,
    "text": "where?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 573.839,
    "end": 581.12,
    "text": " The beach. We can look far at the sea.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 579.04,
    "end": 583.12,
    "text": " The sea?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 581.12,
    "end": 587.6,
    "text": "That sounds good.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 583.12,
    "end": 589.839,
    "text": " Yes, the sea will relax you.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 587.6,
    "end": 593.8,
    "text": " Okay,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 589.839,
    "end": 593.8,
    "text": "let's go to the beach.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 593.839,
    "end": 603.6,
    "text": " Here we are, Tom. This is the beach.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 598.8,
    "end": 607.68,
    "text": " Wow, the sea is so big.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 603.6,
    "end": 612.32,
    "text": " Yes, it's wide and open.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 607.68,
    "end": 617.04,
    "text": " Wide and open. I like that.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 612.32,
    "end": 622.0,
    "text": " Look at the waves. They never stop.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 617.04,
    "end": 626.079,
    "text": " The waves never stop. Always moving.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 622.0,
    "end": 627.92,
    "text": " Right. The sea is alive.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 626.079,
    "end": 631.04,
    "text": "Alive.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 627.92,
    "end": 632.56,
    "text": "You mean it never sleeps?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 631.04,
    "end": 635.12,
    "text": " Exactly.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 632.56,
    "end": 639.279,
    "text": "It never sleeps.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 635.12,
    "end": 642.16,
    "text": " It feels new to me. I usually just see",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 639.279,
    "end": 646.079,
    "text": "pictures on my phone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 642.16,
    "end": 647.76,
    "text": " Now you see it with your eyes, not a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 646.079,
    "end": 652.16,
    "text": "screen.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 647.76,
    "end": 655.44,
    "text": " Yes, with my eyes, not a screen.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 652.16,
    "end": 659.76,
    "text": " Let's sit here on the sand.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 655.44,
    "end": 662.56,
    "text": "Okay. The sand is soft.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 659.76,
    "end": 665.839,
    "text": " Soft and warm.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 662.56,
    "end": 670.32,
    "text": " Yes. Soft and warm.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 665.839,
    "end": 675.12,
    "text": " Take off your shoes. Feel it better.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 670.32,
    "end": 679.839,
    "text": " All right. Wow. It feels good.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 675.12,
    "end": 681.36,
    "text": " See? No phone. Just the sea and the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 679.839,
    "end": 685.68,
    "text": "sand.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 681.36,
    "end": 690.24,
    "text": " No phone. Just the sea and the sand.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 685.68,
    "end": 694.24,
    "text": " Look at those people. They take photos.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 690.24,
    "end": 696.88,
    "text": " Yes. Many photos with their phones.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 694.24,
    "end": 699.6,
    "text": " But we don't need that.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 696.88,
    "end": 704.32,
    "text": " We don't. Why not?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 699.6,
    "end": 707.6,
    "text": " Because we remember with our hearts.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 704.32,
    "end": 709.279,
    "text": " Remember with our hearts, not with",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 707.6,
    "end": 710.88,
    "text": "photos.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 709.279,
    "end": 714.88,
    "text": " Exactly.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 710.88,
    "end": 717.92,
    "text": "A memory is better than a picture.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 714.88,
    "end": 721.279,
    "text": " H maybe you're right.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 717.92,
    "end": 724.0,
    "text": " The sun is going down now.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 721.279,
    "end": 728.8,
    "text": " The colors are beautiful.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 724.0,
    "end": 732.56,
    "text": " Yes. Orange and pink in the sky.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 728.8,
    "end": 736.16,
    "text": " Orange and pink. I like it.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 732.56,
    "end": 738.079,
    "text": " Listen to the sound of the waves.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 736.16,
    "end": 739.839,
    "text": " It's calm.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 738.079,
    "end": 742.72,
    "text": "Very calm.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 739.839,
    "end": 746.079,
    "text": "Do you feel relaxed now?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 742.72,
    "end": 748.16,
    "text": " Yes, very relaxed.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 746.079,
    "end": 752.88,
    "text": "I don't miss my phone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 748.16,
    "end": 755.92,
    "text": " That's great. You see, one day without a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 752.88,
    "end": 759.6,
    "text": "phone is possible.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 755.92,
    "end": 762.399,
    "text": " Yes, possible and peaceful.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 759.6,
    "end": 764.56,
    "text": " Peaceful is the right word.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 762.399,
    "end": 766.16,
    "text": " I feel free.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 764.56,
    "end": 768.8,
    "text": "Really free.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 766.16,
    "end": 772.0,
    "text": " Free and happy.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 768.8,
    "end": 775.76,
    "text": "Yes. Free and happy.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 772.0,
    "end": 779.6,
    "text": " Let's enjoy this moment.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 775.76,
    "end": 783.44,
    "text": " Yes. Let's enjoy this moment.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 779.6,
    "end": 787.6,
    "text": " The sun is going down, Tom.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 783.44,
    "end": 790.16,
    "text": " Yes. The sky is orange now.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 787.6,
    "end": 792.16,
    "text": " It's evening. Do you want to do",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 790.16,
    "end": 794.399,
    "text": "something else?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 792.16,
    "end": 799.2,
    "text": " Something else.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 794.399,
    "end": 801.519,
    "text": "Like what? Let's go to the cinema.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 799.2,
    "end": 803.839,
    "text": " The cinema.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 801.519,
    "end": 809.04,
    "text": "A big screen movie.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 803.839,
    "end": 811.76,
    "text": " Yes. A big screen, not a small phone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 809.04,
    "end": 814.639,
    "text": " H.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 811.76,
    "end": 816.72,
    "text": "That's different.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 814.639,
    "end": 820.399,
    "text": "That sounds exciting.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 816.72,
    "end": 822.639,
    "text": " Great. Let's go see a movie.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 820.399,
    "end": 826.6,
    "text": " Okay.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 822.639,
    "end": 826.6,
    "text": "Let's go to the cinema.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 826.8,
    "end": 836.24,
    "text": "Here we are, Tom. This is the cinema.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 831.76,
    "end": 841.199,
    "text": " It looks big with many lights inside.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 836.24,
    "end": 845.839,
    "text": " Yes. This area is called the lobby.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 841.199,
    "end": 851.279,
    "text": " Lobby. Do you mean the entrance hall?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 845.839,
    "end": 855.92,
    "text": " Exactly. The place before the theater.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 851.279,
    "end": 860.24,
    "text": "Oh, so many movie posters on the wall.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 855.92,
    "end": 862.0,
    "text": " Yes, posters show what movies are",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 860.24,
    "end": 866.959,
    "text": "playing.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 862.0,
    "end": 871.6,
    "text": " Playing you mean showing now or soon.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 866.959,
    "end": 875.36,
    "text": " Right. Showing now or very soon.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 871.6,
    "end": 881.36,
    "text": " And you already got two tickets for us?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 875.36,
    "end": 885.68,
    "text": " Yes, two tickets. We are ready to go.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 881.36,
    "end": 887.199,
    "text": "Okay, let's go inside and find our",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 885.68,
    "end": 890.399,
    "text": "seats.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 887.199,
    "end": 891.839,
    "text": " It's dark here, even before the movie",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 890.399,
    "end": 895.36,
    "text": "starts.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 891.839,
    "end": 896.88,
    "text": " Yes, it's always dark for the big",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 895.36,
    "end": 901.76,
    "text": "screen.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 896.88,
    "end": 906.48,
    "text": " Wow, there are so many seats inside.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 901.76,
    "end": 910.0,
    "text": " Ours are in row six, in the middle.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 906.48,
    "end": 911.36,
    "text": " Row six, in the middle. That sounds",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 910.0,
    "end": 916.639,
    "text": "good.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 911.36,
    "end": 920.88,
    "text": " Sit here. We can see the screen clearly.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 916.639,
    "end": 924.72,
    "text": " Good view. You mean a clear picture?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 920.88,
    "end": 926.32,
    "text": " Yes, a very clear picture from this",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 924.72,
    "end": 931.12,
    "text": "spot.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 926.32,
    "end": 935.44,
    "text": " Wow, the screen looks really huge.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 931.12,
    "end": 940.16,
    "text": " Much bigger than a phone or a TV.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 935.44,
    "end": 944.639,
    "text": "Yes, I feel small under the big screen.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 940.16,
    "end": 949.6,
    "text": " Look, Tom, the movie is starting now.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 944.639,
    "end": 953.519,
    "text": " Oh, the sound is so loud and strong.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 949.6,
    "end": 954.959,
    "text": " Yes, it feels like you are inside the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 953.519,
    "end": 958.32,
    "text": "story.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 954.959,
    "end": 959.839,
    "text": " Loud and strong, not like my little",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 958.32,
    "end": 964.399,
    "text": "phone,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 959.839,
    "end": 967.839,
    "text": " right? A phone is too small and weak.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 964.399,
    "end": 969.36,
    "text": "The picture is bright. I see every",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 967.839,
    "end": 974.32,
    "text": "detail.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 969.36,
    "end": 978.56,
    "text": " Yes, the big screen is very clear.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 974.32,
    "end": 982.959,
    "text": " This is exciting. I really enjoy it.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 978.56,
    "end": 986.88,
    "text": " Good. You enjoy the cinema now.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 982.959,
    "end": 992.56,
    "text": " Yes. More than watching on my phone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 986.88,
    "end": 998.0,
    "text": " See, a cinema is a special experience.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 992.56,
    "end": 1002.399,
    "text": "Yes. Special and amazing. I like it.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 998.0,
    "end": 1006.72,
    "text": " Let's sit back and enjoy the story.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1002.399,
    "end": 1010.72,
    "text": " Yes. Let's enjoy it together.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1006.72,
    "end": 1012.88,
    "text": " The movie is finished. Tom, did you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1010.72,
    "end": 1018.399,
    "text": "enjoy it?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1012.88,
    "end": 1020.8,
    "text": " Yes, I enjoyed it a lot. The big screen",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1018.399,
    "end": 1024.24,
    "text": "was amazing.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1020.8,
    "end": 1029.52,
    "text": "I'm glad you liked it.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1024.24,
    "end": 1032.079,
    "text": " Now we are walking home. The city looks",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1029.52,
    "end": 1036.4,
    "text": "different at night.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1032.079,
    "end": 1038.959,
    "text": " Yes, the street lights make everything",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1036.4,
    "end": 1042.079,
    "text": "soft and warm",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1038.959,
    "end": 1043.6,
    "text": " and the tall buildings are full of",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1042.079,
    "end": 1049.2,
    "text": "lights.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1043.6,
    "end": 1054.32,
    "text": " The city feels alive even at night.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1049.2,
    "end": 1058.64,
    "text": "It feels calm to walk without a phone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1054.32,
    "end": 1060.64,
    "text": " Yes, you can see more when your hands",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1058.64,
    "end": 1067.44,
    "text": "are free.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1060.64,
    "end": 1069.36,
    "text": " I saw more today and I thought more too.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1067.44,
    "end": 1074.72,
    "text": " Like what?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1069.36,
    "end": 1078.48,
    "text": " Like life can be full without a phone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1074.72,
    "end": 1082.88,
    "text": " That's a very good thought.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1078.48,
    "end": 1085.2,
    "text": "I was nervous this morning, but now I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1082.88,
    "end": 1090.08,
    "text": "feel calm.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1085.2,
    "end": 1095.28,
    "text": " So, your day changed step by step.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1090.08,
    "end": 1098.16,
    "text": " Yes. The library, the beach, the cinema,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1095.28,
    "end": 1101.84,
    "text": "all without a phone.",
    "textdich": ""
